reviews.review_text: my  first east coast show a sweet welcome for the heads remember the free camping on private property. the local media was in disbelief as thousands of heads created a city on a nearby deadheads farm. nitrus, tents,school busses sweet misty night . I will never forget that show I could hear every lick in the parking lot didn't even need a ticket to be dancin in the streets unbelievable bliss.
Excellent performance,  fairly ordinary setlist, OK recording.
